The '''CoCo Penitentiary''' was a [[Prison/Legends|prison]] located in [[CoCo Town/Legends|CoCo Town]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], the [[CoCo District Constabulary]] issued a jailbreak alert when three convicts escaped from the Moderate Security Ward of the CoCo Penitentiary. Felons [[Dannl Faytonni/Legends|Dannl Faytonni]], [[Achk Med-Beq/Legends|Achk Med-Beq]] and [[Borlovian]] smuggler [[Llollulion]] escaped aboard a supply truck servicing the Penitentiary's laundry wing.

